                    Materials
                </h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        One or two batteries.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        3 switches
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        3 light bulbs
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Many wires
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ol class = 'questionList'>
                    <li class = 'question'>
                        Construct a circuit with two light bulbs and two switches.
                        Switch A controls both light bulbs,
                        but switch B controls only one light bulb.
                    </li>
                    <li class = 'question'>
                        Construct a circuit with two light bulbs and two switches.
                        Each switch controls one of the two light bulbs,
                        so that each bulb is controlled by a different switch.
                    </li>
                    <li class = 'question'>
                        Construct a circuit with three light bulbs and three switches.
                        Switch A controls one light bulb,
                        switch B controls two light bulbs,
                        and switch C controls all three light bulbs.
                    </li>
                    <li class = 'question'>
                        Construct a circuit with three light bulbs and three switches.
                        Each switch controls a single light bulb,
                        so that each bulb is controlled by a different switch.
                    </li>
                    <li class = 'question'>
                        Construct a circuit with three light bulbs and three switches.
                        Switch A controls light bulb A.
                        Switch B controls light bulb B.
                        Switch C controls light bulbs B and C.
                        (Make sure each bulb and switch are labeled in your diagram.)
                    </li>
                </ol>

            </div>
